title: What's this connector type?
content: Does anybody know this kind of connector? It is used as a diagnostic connector on diesel engines. Inner diameter 15mm, outer 19mm.

answers_data.content:
This is an industrial type ITT Cannon KPT01E12-10S, like this one:

https://www.westfloridacomponents.com/C069APP10/KPT01E12-10S+10+Pos.+Circular+Connector+Receptacle+ITT+Cannon.html

This connector is used for CAN bus communication, which can be used for diagnostics, among other applications.
